         <abstract>
            <p>
               Short hymn starting with words <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ አብል፡ ለ</foreign> or <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለ...</foreign>
               There is a confusion here, since <foreign xml:lang="gez">malkəʾ</foreign> also include the words <foreign xml:lang="gez">salām la-</foreign>,
               and there are longer composition with stanzas starting with <foreign xml:lang="gez">salām la-</foreign>.
            </p>
            <p>An example is:
               <list>
                  <item><p><ref type="mss" corresp="ESday008"/>, f. 37r: <foreign xml:lang="gez">: ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምከ፡ ለዓለም፡ ዘይሄሉ። ለነብይ፡ በከመ፡ ባህሉ። ንጉሥ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ያሳይ፡</foreign>.</p></item>
               </list></p>
         </abstract>
